# General Project Rules
- Automatically commit in English after each change
- Use simple, understandable file names
- Commit frequently after changes (commit often but DO NOT push to GitHub)

# UI/UX Design Rules
- Follow Google Drive-like UI design patterns:
  - Clean, modern interface
  - White background
  - Subtle shadows
  - Rounded corners
- Implement comprehensive file management features:
  - Drag-and-drop functionality
  - Context menus for file operations
  - Breadcrumb navigation
  - Responsive design optimized for Windows file system
  - Toggle between grid and list views
  - File preview capabilities
  - AJAX interactions while maintaining Flask backend compatibility
